<br>
The only bitch I have about having to ask anyone else in Norath to do anything for me, is when im ignored. I will ask a shaman, druid, for sow (note, never a ranger for some reason) and they dont even return reply. just go aobut thier business as if you were on thier /ignore list. I ask extremely politely for any service be it port, sow, invis or anything else. If you dont have time, or you cant do it for some reason, just prove to me you have balls and say NO. I will still thank you very much for talking to me and be on my way. But ignoring a perfectly polite reply bothers me ;-) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/upemadil.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Pemadil </A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Veteran</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/31/02 4:56:42 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=864.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> SAme here, when i  would pay 70pp+ for a port, i would think the 1.5pp regent is included <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   If not, ill walk or find another willing wizard. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/udyschord.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dyschord</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Veteran</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/31/02 8:53:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=864.topic&index=23>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://a6.cpimg.com/image/FC/E7/8157436-35d3-00470051-.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Do you carry your own supply 