Not everyone can buy portal fragments.<br>
<br>
Granted, the majority can, but due to boredom, I know a few people who have waxed that Sol Temple Faction. Only takes a few kills in there to make you KoS. <br>
<br>
I killed that faction before Kunark was even in the game, but I also know how to get it back (It's a pain in the ass, and kinda costly, but it can be done.)<br>
<br>
So sure, for the majority, that's fine. Just remember, there are some people who didn't know that they would ever &quot;need&quot; to step foot in Sol Temple for anything useful.<br>
